  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice + an image. Capture: macOS app / Final Cut screenshot. Draft until imaged. -->\n<p class=\"\">Concept-tagged FCPXML markers for Final Cut Pro. Drops markers at every concept-relevant moment in your transcript so you can navigate hours of footage with Ctrl+' instead of scrubbing.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Resolving and shelling out to whisper for word-level transcription\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/clipgoblin/code.png\" alt=\"Resolving and shelling out to whisper for word-level transcription\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/clipgoblin/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/clipgoblin/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/clipgoblin/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/clipgoblin/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Resolving and shelling out to whisper for word-level transcription\" width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.54deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Resolving and shelling out to whisper for word-level transcription</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The CLI — generating concept-tagged FCPXML markers from a words.json transcript\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/clipgoblin/code2.png\" alt=\"The CLI — generating concept-tagged FCPXML markers from a words.json transcript\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/ima